import p2_img from './product_2.png'

let data_product = [
  {
    id:1,
    name:"Striped Flutter Sleeve Overlap Collar Peplum Hem Blouse",

    old_price:80.50,

    name:"Striped Flutter Sleeve Overlap Collar Peplum Hem Blouse",

  {id:3,
    name:"Striped Flutter Sleeve Overlap Collar Peplum Hem Blouse",

    old_price:100.50,
  },
  {id:4,
    name:"Striped Flutter Sleeve Overlap Collar Peplum Hem Blouse",
    image:p4_img,
    new_price:100.00,
    old_price:150.00,
  },
];

export default data_product;
